<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BPL EKOSİSTEMİ | VR ve Bio-Teknoloji</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Rajdhani:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root { --neon-green: #39FF14; --neon-blue: #00f3ff; --dark-bg: #050a0f; }
        
        body { 
            background: var(--dark-bg); 
            color: white; 
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            background: url('/caracter/page/welcome.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        /* Arka plan karartma perdesi */
        .overlay { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: -1; }

        .navbar-brand img { border: 1px solid var(--neon-green); border-radius: 5px; }

        /* Neon Kartlar */
        .scifi-card {
            background: rgba(10, 15, 20, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.3);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--neon-blue);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .scifi-card:hover { border-color: var(--neon-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.2); }

        .scifi-card.green { border-left-color: var(--neon-green); border-color: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3); }

        /* Destek Merkezi Formu */
        .support-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--neon-green);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
        }
        .form-control { 
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid #333; color: white;
            font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .form-control:focus { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-color: var(--neon-green); color: white; box-shadow: none; }

        .btn-neon-green { 
            background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--neon-green); color: var(--neon-green);
            font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.4s;
        }
        .btn-neon-green:hover { background: var(--neon-green); color: black; box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-green); }

        /* Modal Stilleri (Giriş ve Üye Ol) */
        .modal-content { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue); color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark p-3">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                <img src="/caracter/page/Logo.jpeg" width="45" height="45" alt="BPL Logo">
            </a>
            <div>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info me-2" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#loginModal">GİRİŞ YAP</button>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-neon-green" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#registerModal">ÜYE OL</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--neon-green); font-size: 3.5rem; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.5);">BPL EKOSİSTEMİ</h1>
            <p class="lead text-uppercase tracking-widest">Oyuncuların Efsaneye Dönüştüğü Yer</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="scifi-card">
                    <span class="badge bg-info mb-2">SİSTEM</span>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--neon-blue);">BAŞLIK 1</h3>
                    <p>Buraya açıklama metni gelecek. Turkuaz ve beyazın uyumu neon efektleriyle birleşti.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="scifi-card green">
                    <span class="badge bg-success mb-2">STRATEJİ</span>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--neon-green);">BAŞLIK 2</h3>
                    <p>İkinci kutu içeriği buraya gelecek. Neon detaylar kutu kenarlarında kendini gösteriyor.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="support-box mt-5">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-family: 'Orbitron'; color: var(--neon-green);">BPL DESTEK MERKEZİ</h2>
                    <form id="supportForm">
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Adınız">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <select class="form-control">
                                    <option>Genel Destek</option>
                                    <option>Bakiye Sorunu</option>
                                    <option>Hesap Kurtarma</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Lütfen bu alanı doldurun."></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-neon-green w-100">MESAJI MERKEZE GÖNDER</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="modal fade" id="registerModal" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header border-0"><h5 class="modal-title">HESAP OLUŞTUR (2500 BPL BONUS)</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
                <div class="modal-body p-4">
                    <form action="/register" method="POST">
                        <input type="text" name="nickname" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Nickname" required>
                        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="E-posta" required>
                        <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Şifre" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-neon-green w-100">KAYDI TAMAMLA</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <script>
        // Form gönderimi sonrası uyarılar
        document.getElementById('supportForm').addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            Swal.fire({
                title: 'İLETİLDİ!',
                text: 'Mesajın BPL merkezine ulaştı.',
                icon: 'success',
                background: '#0a0a0a', color: '#fff'
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
